<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><a><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi&nbsp;</span></a><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">{!Contact.FirstName},<br></span><br>You elected to pay for your Kingsbridge business insurance policy&nbsp;<b>{!Policy__c.Name}&nbsp;</b>through direct debit payments.&nbsp;<br><b><br>Our credit providers Close Brothers Premium Finance required you to consent to the commission Kingsbridge receive in order to provide the loan for your insurance policy.&nbsp;<br></b><br>Close Brothers have sent you numerous communications via email, SMS and physical letter to notify you of this requirement.&nbsp;<br><b><i><br>You have not provided this consent/You have declined to consent</i>&nbsp;and so Close Brothers have now rejected your credit application.&nbsp;<u>This means the payment for your insurance policy remains outstanding.&nbsp;<br></u></b><b><font size="4"><br>What are your options?</font></b><br></font></p><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Make your outstanding payment in full to Kingsbridge&nbsp;</b><br>You can make a payment by credit or debit card. We also accept cardless payments via GoCardless. To make your payment please contact our customer service team on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>&nbsp;and select option 3.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Re-apply for a loan with Close Brothers</b><br>If you are happy to provide commission consent, it may be possible to apply for a new loan with Close Brothers to cover your outstanding payment. To re-apply for a loan with Close Brothers please contact our customer service team on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>&nbsp;and select option 3.</font></li></ul><p class="MsoNormal"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font size="4"><b>What happens if I don’t make the payment?<br></b></font><b><u><br>If a payment has not been made before&nbsp;<i>[proposed cancellation date]</i>, your policy will be cancelled from inception.&nbsp;<br></u></b><u><br>Please be aware, if the policy is cancelled from inception, your business will not be insured and you will not be able to make a claim under it as it will be considered null and void.</u>&nbsp;<br><br>To help your business stay protected, please call us on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>&nbsp;to make a payment or discuss further.<br><u><br>Please note, for data security reasons, do not send credit or debit card details to us via email.<br></u><br>Kind regards,<br><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">T: 01242 808 740</span></font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>